channel.title: Ricky Wilson's Art Jam
channel.desc: Vlogger and Strictly star Joe Sugg visits the Art Jam studio to show Ricky three items that mean the world to him - a sketch pad full of his own incredible drawings, a model campervan and a homemade clay monster. While chatting to Ricky, Joe shares amazing stories about his online career, a lifelong love of art and childhood memories of growing up in the countryside with sister Zoe - aka Zoella.
